ahead with this, you know.

21:00.391 --> 21:01.459
Yeah, I know.

21:01.491 --> 21:04.561
But I don't want them
dying in vain.

21:04.595 --> 21:07.432
Now if...
if I do this show,

21:07.464 --> 21:09.900
