21:15.807 --> 21:17.608
to appreciate what we've got,

21:17.642 --> 21:20.312
to foster empathy.

21:20.345 --> 21:22.579
And it's not gonna be
about fame or money,

21:22.613 --> 21:25.583
and we are not gonna be
bribing guests to come on.

21:25.615 --> 21:27.585
They will come
of their own volition.

21:27.617 --> 21:29.486
