from the parking lot,

22:48.665 --> 22:50.934
so no one behind that wall
can get into the audience.

22:50.968 --> 22:53.037
Who is in charge here?
You or him?

22:53.069 --> 22:55.773
I am.

22:55.807 --> 22:56.908
I am.

22:56.942 --> 22:59.109
It's not about death,
but it is about ratings.

22:59.143 --> 23:02.646
The idea here is
to have people wake up.

23:05.549 --> 23:06.717
He looks like a serial killer.

23:06.750 --> 23:08.086
