23:08.118 --> 23:09.586
Well, he can serial
kill himself.

23:09.619 --> 23:11.855
We're making this
network relevant.

23:11.888 --> 23:12.656
You cannot forget.

23:12.690 --> 23:14.692
Can we order some pizza, please?

23:14.724 --> 23:18.663
This is where I wanna start,
what's next... nope.

23:18.695 --> 23:20.932
And we're gonna need to work
on these screens here, right?

23:36.180 --> 23:38.716
What are we doing here?

23:38.749 --> 23:40.151
What are we doing here?
- Mm-hmm.

23:40.183 --> 23:43.721
Uh... we're making a show.

23:43.753 --> 23:45.589
You know what I mean.

23:47.491 --> 23:49.493
We're giving television the
kick in the ass that it needs.

23:49.527 --> 23:50.694
That's what we're doing here.

23:50.728 --> 23:53.131
We're challenging people to get
up and stand for something.

23:53.163 --> 23:54.499
And what is that? Death?

23:54.531 --> 23:57.868
No. No, Sylvia.
Life.

24:00.738 --> 24:03.641
It's not just a show
about death.

24:03.673 --> 24:05.943
<i>You do know that no one
at the network</i>

24:05.977 --> 24:09.147
