- Yeah.

24:09.180 --> 24:13.116
They just want shock and awe
and blood and pyrotechnics.

24:13.150 --> 24:14.384
Yeah, I know. I know,

24:14.417 --> 24:18.756
but I think that we can create a
scenario where everybody wins.

24:20.590 --> 24:22.526
God, I want to believe you.

24:22.559 --> 24:23.861
You know, for a reality
show veteran,

24:23.894 --> 24:26.698
you are impressively naive.

24:26.730 --> 24:31.502
Yeah? Well, for a woman who
tells fairytales for a living,

24:31.536 --> 24:33.671
your lack of imagination
is quite sad.

24:37.807 --> 24:38.977
Knock 'em dead, kiddo.

24:40.978 --> 24:42.779
Really?

24:42.813 --> 24:44.215
Let's have a good show,
everybody.

24:44.248 --> 24:46.518
Stand by VTU.

24:48.885 --> 24:52.057
On in five, four, three...

24:55.159 --> 24:56.895
Cue graphics and music.
Cue camera one.

24:58.095 --> 25:02.600
<i>Live from Los Angeles,
This Is Your Death!</i>

25:02.633 --> 25:06.738
<i>And now, your host, Adam Rogers!</i>

25:09.773 --> 25:13.577
Ladies and gentlemen...

25:13.611 --> 25:16.281
What you're about to see tonight

25:16.314 --> 25:18.917
