Hold the prompter.

25:30.027 --> 25:32.197
This is not a prank.

25:34.699 --> 25:39.304
And this will probably
shock you, and that's okay.

25:39.336 --> 25:42.307
Because on this show
we're all about transparency.

25:44.008 --> 25:46.210
Now, despite what most
networks want you to believe,

25:46.242 --> 25:48.745
your television is not there to
coddle you,

25:48.778 --> 25:50.847
nor is it there to provide
mindless escapism.

25:50.881 --> 25:53.317
What is going on?
- He's ad-libbing, is what's going on.

25:53.351 --> 25:55.687
Is this a surprise?
