32:51.367 --> 32:54.504
<i>Thank you for watching
This Is Your Death.</i>

32:56.339 --> 32:58.708
Life is precious.

32:58.741 --> 33:01.077
Make the most of it.

33:01.111 --> 33:02.380
See you next week.

33:26.670 --> 33:29.673
And... cut to commercial.

33:43.519 --> 33:44.754
Everyone's phones still off?

33:44.788 --> 33:47.223
Yeah.

33:47.257 --> 33:48.558
Congratulations.

33:48.592 --> 33:51.295
