network $100,000.

33:51.327 --> 33:52.328
We raised $100,000?

33:52.362 --> 33:54.298
$200,000 actually.

33:54.330 --> 33:56.132
But we only had to
match up to $100,000.

33:56.165 --> 33:59.803
Wait, wait, wait. So we just
gave that girl $300,000?

33:59.836 --> 34:02.440
Yes.
- Wow!

34:02.472 --> 34:03.574
That's good!

34:03.606 --> 34:06.309
Is this show now about money?

34:06.343 --> 34:09.547
No, this is a show about giving
girls like that a future.

34:09.579 --> 34:11.181
By killing her mother.

34:11.215 --> 34:12.681
Sara died of her own volition

34:12.715 --> 34:15.219
after consulting a trained
psychiatrist and physician,

34:15.251 --> 34:17.822
and, because of it, she bettered
the life of her daughter.

34:17.855 --> 34:19.422
That's right.

34:19.456 --> 34:20.422
By killing herself.

