34:29.500 --> 34:32.369
Look, not everything in this
world deserves a happy ending.

34:32.402 --> 34:35.139
Sophocles knew this.
Euripides knew this.

34:35.172 --> 34:37.108
Shakespeare knew this.
Milton, Beckett...

34:37.141 --> 34:38.842
What-- what're you doing?

34:38.876 --> 34:40.011
